text: Caspar Cornelis Johannes Veldkamp (born 23 April 1964) is a Dutch politician and former diplomat who has been the Minister of Foreign Affairs since 2024. Veldkamp was a member of the House of Representatives for the New Social Contract party from December 2023 to July 2024. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1964 births Category:Ministers of foreign affairs of the Netherlands Category:Ambassadors of the Netherlands Category:Members of the House of Representatives of the Netherlands Category:Christian Democratic Appeal politicians Category:Politicians from North Brabant
